sql_statement.static: SELECT
as IterationNum,
as FrameSize,
as IntendedLoad,
as Duration,
as ExpectedShortPercent,
as ExpectedLongPercent,
as ExpectedCrcPercent, 1 as ErrorType,

sum(GeneratorPortResults.GeneratorUndersizeFrameCount) as TxFrameCount, sum(AnalyzerPortResults.UndersizeFrameCount) as UndersizeCount,  sum(AnalyzerPortResults.OversizeFrameCount) as OversizeCount,  sum(AnalyzerPortResults.FcsErrorFrameCount) as CrcErrorCount, case when sum(GeneratorPortResults.GeneratorUndersizeFrameCount) > 0 then round(sum(AnalyzerPortResults.UndersizeFrameCount) / sum(GeneratorPortResults.GeneratorUndersizeFrameCount)* 100 , 2) else 0 end as ActualShortPercent, case when sum(GeneratorPortResults.GeneratorOversizeFrameCount) > 0 then round(sum(AnalyzerPortResults.OversizeFrameCount) / sum(GeneratorPortResults.GeneratorOversizeFrameCount) * 100, 2) else 0 end as ActualLongPercent, case when sum(GeneratorPortResults.GeneratorCrcErrorFrameCount) > 0 then round(sum(AnalyzerPortResults.FcsErrorFrameCount) / sum(GeneratorPortResults.GeneratorCrcErrorFrameCount) * 100, 2) else 0 end as ActualCrcPercent  FROM  AnalyzerPortResults, Port, Analyzer , GeneratorPortResults, Generator WHERE  AnalyzerPortResults.ParentHnd = Analyzer.Handle AND   Analyzer.ParentHnd = Port.Handle AND  GeneratorPortResults.ParentHnd = Generator.Handle AND Generator.ParentHnd = Port.Handle

columns: IterationNum, FrameSize, IntendedLoad, Duration, ErrorType, TxFrameCount, UndersizeCount, OversizeCount, CrcErrorCount, ExpectedShortPercent, ActualShortPercent, ExpectedLongPercent, ActualLongPercent, ExpectedCrcPercent, ActualCrcPercent

update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set Enabled = (select case when 1 in (select ErrorType from Rfc2889ErroredFramesFilteringPerLoadResult) then 'True' else 'False' end) where ID = 1
update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set FrameSize = (select value as 'Frame Size' from spirent_methodology_SetPropertyCommand where name = 'Set Short Frame Size') where ID = 1

update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set Duration = (select WaitTime as 'Duration' from WaitCommand where ParentHnd = (select Handle from SequencerIfCommand where Id = 5) and Name = 'Trial Duration' ) where ID = 1

update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set ExpectedForwardedFrameCount = (select value as '% Expected Forwarded Frame Count' from spirent_methodology_SetPropertyCommand where Name = 'Configure Expected Forwarded Short Frames in iteration results') where ID = 1

update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set IterationNum = (select ROUND(MaxVal,0) from spirent_methodology_ObjectIteratorCommand where Handle = (select ExpressionCommand from spirent_methodology_IterationWhileCommand where IterationName = 'Trial')) where ID = 1
update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set Enabled = (select case when 2 in (select ErrorType from Rfc2889ErroredFramesFilteringPerLoadResult) then 'True' else 'False' end) where ID = 2
update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set FrameSize = (select value as 'Frame Size' from spirent_methodology_SetPropertyCommand where name = 'Set Long Frame Size') where ID = 2

update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set Duration = (select WaitTime as 'Duration' from WaitCommand where ParentHnd = (select Handle from SequencerIfCommand where Id = 8) and Name = 'Trial Duration' ) where ID = 2

update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set ExpectedForwardedFrameCount = (select value as '% Expected Forwarded Frame Count' from spirent_methodology_SetPropertyCommand where Name = 'Configure Expected Forwarded Long Frames in iteration results') where ID = 2

update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set IterationNum = (select ROUND(MaxVal,0) from spirent_methodology_ObjectIteratorCommand where Handle = (select ExpressionCommand from spirent_methodology_IterationWhileCommand where IterationName = 'Trial')) where ID = 2
update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set Enabled = (select case when 0 in (select ErrorType from Rfc2889ErroredFramesFilteringPerLoadResult) then 'True' else 'False' end ) where ID = 3

update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set Duration = (select WaitTime as 'Duration' from WaitCommand where ParentHnd = (select Handle from SequencerIfCommand where Id = 11) and Name = 'Trial Duration' ) where ID = 3

update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set ExpectedForwardedFrameCount = (select value as '% Expected Forwarded Frame Count' from spirent_methodology_SetPropertyCommand where Name = 'Configure Expected Forwarded CRC Errored Frames in iteration results') where ID = 3

update MethRfc2889EFFConfig set IterationNum = (select ROUND(MaxVal,0) from spirent_methodology_ObjectIteratorCommand where Handle = (select ExpressionCommand from spirent_methodology_IterationWhileCommand where IterationName = 'Trial')) where ID = 3

Properties.Name: SqlQuery
Properties.Value: SELECT ErroredFrameType as 'Errored Frame Type', Enabled as 'Enabled', IterationNum as 'Number of trials', FrameSize as 'Frame Size (bytes)', Duration as 'Trial Duration (s)', ExpectedForwardedFrameCount as '% Expected Forwarded Frame Count' from MethRfc2889EFFConfig

Properties.Name: PassedVerdictExplanation
Properties.Value: Configuration Details for each type of errored frame

Properties.Name: SqlQuery
Properties.Value: select  IterationNum as 'Iteration', IntendedLoad as 'Load Level (%)',  sum(case when ErrorType = 1 then TxFrameCount else 0 end) as 'Tx''d Short Frame Count', sum(case when ErrorType = 1 then UndersizeCount else 0 end) as 'Rx''d Short Frame Count',  sum(case when ErrorType = 2 then TxFrameCount else 0 end) as 'Tx''d Long Frame Count', sum(case when ErrorType = 2 then OversizeCount else 0 end) as 'Rx''d Long Frame Count',  sum(case when ErrorType = 0 then TxFrameCount else 0 end) as 'Tx''d CRC Errored Frame Count', sum(case when ErrorType = 0 then CrcErrorCount else 0 end) as 'Rx''d CRC Errored Frame Count',  case when ErrorType = 0 and ActualCrcPercent <= ExpectedCrcPercent  or ErrorType = 1 and ActualShortPercent <= ExpectedShortPercent or ErrorType = 2 and ActualLongPercent <= ExpectedLongPercent then 'PASS'  else 'FAIL' end as 'Iteration Result'  from  Rfc2889ErroredFramesFilteringPerLoadResult  group by IterationNum, IntendedLoad

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT name FROM sqlite_master

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: Short Frames did not meet the expected forwarding percentage

sql_statement.static: SELECT IterationNum as 'Iteration', IntendedLoad as 'Load Level (%)', Duration as 'Duration (s)',
as 'Short Frame Size (bytes)',
sum(case when ErrorType = 1 then TxFrameCount else 0 end) as 'Transmitted Short Frame Count',
sum(case when ErrorType = 1 then UndersizeCount else 0 end) as 'Received Short Frame Count',
sum(case when ErrorType = 1 then ExpectedShortPercent else 0 end) as '% Expected Forwarded Short Frame Count',
sum(case when ErrorType = 1 then ActualShortPercent else 0 end) as '% Actual Forwarded Short Frame Count'
FROM Rfc2889ErroredFramesFilteringPerLoadResult
WHERE  ActualShortPercent > ExpectedShortPercent group by IterationNum, IntendedLoad
